---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="关于探索中国" lang="zh" alternateHref="/about" alternateLabel="EN" minimalNav={true}>
  <section class="section card tone-sand" style="padding:34px;">
    <p class="pill">关于</p>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,64px); margin-top:10px;">关于 Explore China</h1>
    <p class="muted" style="max-width:860px; font-size:18px;">项目起源说明将在下一轮内容完善中确认。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section card tone-blue">
    <h2 class="section-title">团队成员</h2>
    <div class="grid cols-3">
      <article class="card" style="background:#fff;"><p class="label">成员</p><h3>姓名 01</h3><p class="muted">一句话介绍将在后续确认。</p></article>
      <article class="card" style="background:#fff;"><p class="label">成员</p><h3>姓名 02</h3><p class="muted">一句话介绍将在后续确认。</p></article>
      <article class="card" style="background:#fff;"><p class="label">成员</p><h3>姓名 03</h3><p class="muted">一句话介绍将在后续确认。</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section card tone-rose">
    <h2 class="section-title">我们为什么做这个项目</h2>
    <p class="muted">项目动机说明将在下一轮内容完善中补充为正式版本。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section card" style="margin-bottom:36px;">
    <h2 class="section-title">联系方式</h2>
    <p class="muted">Email: 联系方式待公布</p>
    <p class="muted">Instagram: 账号待公布</p>
    <p class="muted">WeChat: 账号待公布</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
